(128, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/05/wordpress-4-2-2/''>WordPress 4.2.2 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">7 de maio de 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.2.2 is now available. This is a critical security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. Version 4.2.2 addresses two security issues: The Genericons icon font package, which is used in a number of popular themes and plugins, contained an HTML file vulnerable to a cross-site [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/menu-customizer-tentatively-approved-for-wordpress-4-3''>WPTavern: Menu Customizer Tentatively Approved for WordPress 4.3</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/buddydrive-1-3-utilizes-the-new-bp-attachments-api''>WPTavern: BuddyDrive 1.3 Utilizes the New BP Attachments API</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/how-to-add-a-default-image-to-jetpacks-related-posts-module''>WPTavern: How to Add a Default Image to Jetpack’s Related Posts Module</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugins populares:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/responsive-lightbox/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Responsive Lightbox by dFactory</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=responsive-lightbox&amp;_wpnonce=8abdd5a96b&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Responsive Lightbox by dFactory''>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
